snippet.title: Taiko no Tatsujin: Rhythm Festival - Gameplay Trailer | Nintendo Direct
snippet.description:
Become a Taiko master with all your favorite Japanese drum songs including a few Nintendo inspired rhythms when the latest Taiko no Tatsujin game releases later this year.
